text: Kamenný Újezd may refer to the following locations in the Czech Republic: * Kamenný Újezd (České Budějovice District), a village in České Budějovice District * Kamenný Újezd (Rokycany District), a village in Rokycany District == See also == * 12833 Kamenný Újezd, an asteroid
